translation.content:
Translation will only be synced if any one of the entity Article, Section or Categories is selected.

If you stop syncing translation data and start re-syncing it later, the connection will not backfill missing translation records for already synced articles, sections, and categories.

content_id refers to the ID of an Article, Post, Topic, or Section
content_type is either Article, Post, Topic, or Section

generalNotes.content:
# Notes

- Zendesk__ticket_metrics and other models must be created through [Transformations](https://fivetran.com/docs/transformations/data-models/zendesk-support-data-model/zendesk-support-transform-model).
- [Tags](https://support.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/203662096-Using-tags) provide additional context about tickets, organizations and users and are used in automations.
